&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As a Capital Specialist (Inside Sales), you will play a key role in driving revenue by closing business financing deals with small and medium sized business decision makers across a wide range of industries.&lt;/strong&gt; You’ll dive deep into each prospect’s business, understand their needs, and craft a compelling value proposition that showcases how Fora Financial’s solutions can support their growth. This is a high‑impact role designed for a motivated closer who thrives in a fast‑paced sales environment and is excited by &lt;strong&gt;uncapped earning potential&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
